			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A simple description of the bug:
<br />

<br />
If /pet focus is toggled on, and your pet has 2 or more NPCs on it's aggro list, it will break mezzes against whatever it is currently attacking.
<br />

<br />
It breaks them 100% of the time, not just once in a great while.  You'll know when it's happening, because you get spammed by literally about 50 "I am unable to wake Target, Master." messages before he finally breaks mez.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212730" target="_blank" class="postlink">Nirrudn Ak`Lmar</a>,
<br />
<a href="http://www.sok.org" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sterling Order of Knights</a>
<br />
Fennin Ro
